    "description": "<strong>4D Golf</strong> is a mind-bending golf game unlike any other because it's set entirely in a 4-dimensional space. Complete fun and unique golfing challenges as you gain hands-on experience of the 4th dimension and beyond!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147950/extras/897489bcd60281c4ce2575be97ae0a4d.poster.avif?t=1717097197\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147950/extras/897489bcd60281c4ce2575be97ae0a4d.webm?t=1717097197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147950/extras/897489bcd60281c4ce2575be97ae0a4d.mp4?t=1717097197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 120 levels and 7 vibrant themed worlds<br></li><li>Tons of visualization options to master 4D space<br></li><li>Build your own 4D courses in the level editor<br></li><li>Race the clock in Marble Platforming Mode<br></li><li>Navigate hidden paths, moving platforms, shifting gravity, speed boosts, and more!<br></li><li>Unlock custom accessories by completing challenges</li></ul><br>Now open your third eye and unleash your full potential!",
